  case $(menu "Install" "ůįęŹ  Ruby on Rails\n  Docker\n  JavaScript\n  Go\n  PHP\n  Python\n  Elixir\n  Zig\n  Rust\n  Java\n  .NET\n  OCaml\n  Clojure\n  Scala") in
